# worldoracle demo — generate with: vhs assets/demo.tape
# Install vhs: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs  (brew install vhs)

Output assets/demo.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0

# Install
Type "pip install worldoracle" Sleep 500ms Enter
Sleep 2s
Ctrl+L

# TODO: replace below with real demo commands for this project
Type "worldoracle --help" Sleep 300ms Enter
Sleep 3s
